  "content_markdown": "1\n\n###  Application and Definitions\n\n1.1\n\nUnless otherwise stated, this Part applies to:\n\n  1. (1) a _run-off firm_ ;\n  2. (2) a _non-directive insurer_ ; and\n  3. (3) a _Swiss general insurer_.\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2016*\n\n1.2\n\nIn this Part, the following definitions shall apply:\n\n_application rules_\n\nmeans any application rule in any Part in the [Non-Solvency II Firms](/pra-rules/non-sii-firms \"Non-Solvency II Firms\") Sector of the _PRA_ Rulebook.\n\n_run-off firm_\n\nmeans a _firm_ to which, but for the application of [Transitional Measures 2.1](/pra-rules/transitional-measures#ce01c09e148b43cda20c93d1e5e68a59 \"Transitional Measures 2.1\") to [2.3](/pra-rules/transitional-measures#69745ab3af33416894f8f44f0597f027 \"2.3\") in the [Solvency II Firms](/pra-rules/sii-firms \"Solvency II Firms\") Sector, the _Solvency II rules_ would apply.\n\n_Solvency II rules_\n\nmeans the _PRA_ rules in the [Valuation](/pra-rules/valuation \"Valuation\"), [Technical Provisions](/pra-rules/technical-provisions \"Technical Provisions\"), [Own Funds](/pra-rules/own-funds \"Own Funds\"), [Solvency Capital Requirement – General Provisions](/pra-rules/solvency-capital-requirement---general-provisions \"Solvency\n\nCapital Requirement – General Provisions\"), [Solvency Capital Requirement – Standard Formula](/pra-rules/solvency-capital-requirement---standard-formula \"Solvency Capital Requirement – Standard Formula\"), [Solvency Capital Requirement – Internal Models](/pra-rules/solvency-capital-requirement---internal-models \"Solvency Capital Requirement – Internal Models\"), [Minimum Capital Requirement](/pra-rules/minimum-capital-requirement \"Minimum Capital Requirement\"), [Undertakings in Difficulty](/pra-rules/undertakings-in-difficulty \"Undertakings in Difficulty\"), [Investments](/pra-rules/investments \"Investments\"), [Composites](/pra-rules/composites \"Composites\"), [Conditions Governing Business](/pra-rules/conditions-governing-business \"Conditions Governing Business\"), [Insurance Special Purpose Vehicles](/pra-rules/insurance-special-purpose-vehicles \"Insurance Special Purpose Vehicles\"), [Group Supervision](/pra-rules/group-supervision \"Group Supervision\"), [Reporting](/pra-rules/reporting \"Reporting\"), [Surplus Funds](/pra-rules/surplus-funds \"Surplus Funds\"), [With-Profits](/pra-rules/with-profits \"With-Profits\"), [Insurance - Certification](/pra-rules/insurance---certification \"Insurance - Certificatio\"), [Insurance – Conduct Standards](/pra-rules/insurance---conduct-standards \"Insurance – Conduct Standards\"), [Insurance – Senior Management Functions](/pra-rules/insurance---senior-management-functions \"Insurance – Senior Insurance Management Functions\"), [Insurance – Allocation of Responsibilities](/pra-rules/insurance---allocation-of-responsibilities \"Insurance – Allocation of Responsibilities\") and [Insurance – Fitness and Propriety](/pra-rules/insurance---fitness-and-propriety \"Insurance – Fitness and Propriety\") Parts of the [Solvency II Firms](/pra-rules/sii-firms \"Solvency II Firms\") Sector of the _PRA_ Rulebook.\n\n*Effective: 10/12/2018*\n\n2\n\n###  Transitional Applications of Rules in Relation to Run-Off Firms\n\n2.1\n\nNotwithstanding the _application rules_ , each Part in the [Non-Solvency II Firms](/pra-rules/non-sii-firms \"Non-Solvency II Firms\") Sector of the _PRA_ Rulebook applies to a _run-off firm_ for so long as it remains a _run-off firm_ as if the _firm_ was a _non-directive insurer_ and not a _UK Solvency II firm_.\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2016*\n\n3\n\n###  Reporting\n\n3.1\n\nA _firm_ must comply with the rules in:\n\n  1. (1) [IPRU(FSOC)](/pra-rules/ipru-fsoc-interim-prudential-sourcebook-for-friendly-societies \"IPRU\\(FSOC\\)\") Chapter 5; and\n  2. (2) [IPRU(INS)](/pra-rules/ipru-ins-interim-prudential-sourcebook-for-insurers \"IPRU\\(INS\\)\") Chapters 9 and 12\n\nof the _PRA Handbook_ as at 31 December 2015, as they were applicable to the _firm_ (including any _waiver_) at that date, in respect of _financial years_ ending on or before 30 June 2016.\n\n*Effective: 01/07/2016*",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"col9\">\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"part-content\">\n\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"59ee347799e247d29c6769f56a5f9b08\" id=\"a2200707e27049f7b9ae29640f4cd2ec\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t1\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tApplication and Definitions\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"2b7f9234b467459d952fbaf723f9a9ec\" id=\"c659780e4314402191e007e09c5fe35d\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>Unless otherwise stated, this Part applies to:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"77501\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-78508e760a0d4afbb1f836d9379c0b13\" title=\"run-off firm\">run-off firm</a></em>;</li>\n<li>(2) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"77344\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-11da8de4e3ea416bb8732a6f2fe0eb07\" title=\"non-directive insurer\">non-directive insurer</a></em>; and</li>\n<li>(3) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52910\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7ecb61ce28ed4c4e947c300a772aa937\" title=\"Swiss general insurer\">Swiss general insurer</a></em>.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"fa0c902ed43c49eeb3d0f90ff3cc9e9a\" id=\"bf4c3dc215c0497d93b98ad353b57540\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>In this Part, the following definitions shall apply:</p>\n<p><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"77500\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-288521955d4044e7a9eff1ecf9c9b0f8\" title=\"application rules\">application rules</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means any application rule in any Part in the <a data-mce-contenttype=\"2\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-sii-firms\" title=\"Non-Solvency II Firms\">Non-Solvency II Firms</a> Sector of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> Rulebook.</p>\n<p><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"77501\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-78508e760a0d4afbb1f836d9379c0b13\" title=\"run-off firm\">run-off firm</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means a<em> <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> to which, but for the application of <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/transitional-measures#ce01c09e148b43cda20c93d1e5e68a59\" title=\"Transitional Measures 2.1\">Transitional Measures 2.1</a> to <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/transitional-measures#69745ab3af33416894f8f44f0597f027\" title=\"2.3\">2.3</a> in the <a data-mce-contenttype=\"2\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" href=\"/pra-rules/sii-firms\" title=\"Solvency II Firms\">Solvency II Firms</a> Sector, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"77502\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c78ee16cea234c5dbfdc1be317775e13\" title=\"Solvency II rules\">Solvency II rules</a></em> would apply.</p>\n<p><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"77502\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c78ee16cea234c5dbfdc1be317775e13\" title=\"Solvency II rules\">Solvency II rules</a></em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> rules in the <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/valuation\" title=\"Valuation\">Valuation</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/technical-provisions\" title=\"Technical Provisions\">Technical Provisions</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/own-funds\" title=\"Own Funds\">Own Funds</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/solvency-capital-requirement---general-provisions\" title=\"Solvency\n\nCapital Requirement – General Provisions\">Solvency Capital Requirement – General Provisions</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/solvency-capital-requirement---standard-formula\" title=\"Solvency Capital Requirement – Standard Formula\">Solvency Capital Requirement – Standard Formula</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/solvency-capital-requirement---internal-models\" title=\"Solvency Capital Requirement – Internal Models\">Solvency Capital Requirement – Internal Models</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/minimum-capital-requirement\" title=\"Minimum Capital Requirement\">Minimum Capital Requirement</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/undertakings-in-difficulty\" title=\"Undertakings in Difficulty\">Undertakings in Difficulty</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/investments\" title=\"Investments\">Investments</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/composites\" title=\"Composites\">Composites</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/conditions-governing-business\" title=\"Conditions Governing Business\">Conditions Governing Business</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance-special-purpose-vehicles\" title=\"Insurance Special Purpose Vehicles\">Insurance Special Purpose Vehicles</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/group-supervision\" title=\"Group Supervision\">Group Supervision</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/reporting\" title=\"Reporting\">Reporting</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/surplus-funds\" title=\"Surplus Funds\">Surplus Funds</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/with-profits\" title=\"With-Profits\">With-Profits</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---certification\" title=\"Insurance - Certificatio\">Insurance - Certification</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---conduct-standards\" title=\"Insurance – Conduct Standards\">Insurance – Conduct Standards</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---senior-management-functions\" title=\"Insurance – Senior Insurance Management Functions\">Insurance – Senior Management Functions</a>, <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---allocation-of-responsibilities\" title=\"Insurance – Allocation of Responsibilities\">Insurance – Allocation of Responsibilities</a> and <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/insurance---fitness-and-propriety\" title=\"Insurance – Fitness and Propriety\">Insurance – Fitness and Propriety</a> Parts of the <a data-mce-contenttype=\"2\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" href=\"/pra-rules/sii-firms\" title=\"Solvency II Firms\">Solvency II Firms</a> Sector of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> Rulebook.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/nonsolvency-ii-firms-transitional-measures/01-01-2016#bf4c3dc215c0497d93b98ad353b57540\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 1.2 before 10/12/2018\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"f63928b0c2c8442a81b950c9d1d020e5\" id=\"a38c36051ab642309d2ce9150e0047c6\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t2\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tTransitional Applications of Rules in Relation to Run-Off Firms\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"5401c73cfec44701af79eb1a51959c26\" id=\"88335c4a43ad4493bc71597392ed5867\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>Notwithstanding the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"77500\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-288521955d4044e7a9eff1ecf9c9b0f8\" title=\"application rules\">application rules</a></em>, each Part in the <a data-mce-contenttype=\"2\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" href=\"/pra-rules/non-sii-firms\" title=\"Non-Solvency II Firms\">Non-Solvency II Firms</a> Sector of the<em> <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> Rulebook applies to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"77501\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-78508e760a0d4afbb1f836d9379c0b13\" title=\"run-off firm\">run-off firm</a></em> for so long as it remains a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"77501\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-78508e760a0d4afbb1f836d9379c0b13\" title=\"run-off firm\">run-off firm</a></em> as if the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> was a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"77344\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-11da8de4e3ea416bb8732a6f2fe0eb07\" title=\"non-directive insurer\">non-directive insurer</a></em> and not a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52930\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-0d29d447fd4b4fca868c1d2e5b5e2276\" title=\"UK Solvency II firm\">UK Solvency II firm</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"befb3f6eb3c543869850510ca7003c65\" id=\"7643820278694f3ba435870e75136e96\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t3\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tReporting\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"c9a658d212c14d0faac720f91bdaba85\" id=\"01128689795f45f1b44d9e3aa899eaca\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must comply with the rules in:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/ipru-fsoc-interim-prudential-sourcebook-for-friendly-societies\" title=\"IPRU(FSOC)\">IPRU(FSOC)</a> Chapter 5; and</li>\n<li>(2) <a data-mce-contenttype=\"4\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Part\" href=\"/pra-rules/ipru-ins-interim-prudential-sourcebook-for-insurers\" title=\"IPRU(INS)\">IPRU(INS)</a> Chapters 9 and 12</li>\n</ol>\n<p>of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52206\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-10515d7817d74ae181245d1eec49471b\" title=\"PRA Handbook\">PRA Handbook</a></em> as at 31 December 2015, as they were applicable to the<em> <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> (including any <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52973\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-e77d564ee0ed4e2f8fad035aa99f765f\" title=\"waiver\">waiver</a></em>) at that date, in respect of<em> <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"77303\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a3c07cebb1e34b11a18a36c0b80f9e27\" title=\"financial years\">financial years</a></em> ending on or before 30 June 2016.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/07/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/nonsolvency-ii-firms-transitional-measures/01-01-2016#01128689795f45f1b44d9e3aa899eaca\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 3.1 before 01/07/2016\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div>\n</div>",
